Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:49.32,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第6碗  家里煮的饭、冷了也觉得热乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊  问你借了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一口气读完它们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这漫画的确有很多设定不集中  读完一转眼就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊  到一半会分不清敌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为40卷前死掉的角色突然出现我也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  没错啊  什么嘛  你也不是很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  你最喜欢哪个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏奈姐最喜欢哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我可不喜欢那么优柔寡断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着都有点心急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我读完再促膝长谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我很欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重的  我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么点没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好迟啊  出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特殊的事却回来迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟点回来理由这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在照顾仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一和我负责饲养它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  就因为这个啊  真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些漫画是从冬木那借来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还真执着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这部长篇漫画全收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局是成为贵族还是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下冬木就是好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我都用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是尊敬长辈的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬语我还是会用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看对方是谁就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是本质不同啊  明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不管对谁都笑着说敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经积得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷可是女人的天敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可不能掉以轻心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在胡扯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜是久违的大雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp225}　{\fsp1}gratin{\fsp1}{\r}\N两袋冷冻法式奶汁干酪烙菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边只有切片面包和意大利面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些食材真够微妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一手  把剩下的东西全扔进火锅做大杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑会餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃气罐没了  储藏罐也没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要去买菜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经积得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃现成的应付一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那赶紧准备起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一堆漫画要读
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好了叫我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当自己是千金大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了  满足了  开心了  塞满了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一厘米都塞不进了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  几乎把剩下的材料全用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不去补习一定要去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也把这个买了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一包了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺道去下干洗店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了把外套拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁送去的谁去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪还在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  明天明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的天气可出不了门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚刚在电梯口碰到邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是接下来还要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽吐错地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去干洗店拿衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪有没有积起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积得好深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的雪白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷起来了  回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟寒冷是女人的天敌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪天在院子里到处跑才是正解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后打算缩在被炉里吗  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你在那边发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来劲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈选手投出…第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你狠  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进到鼻子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  站起来千秋  你不会就这点本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡扯  我会去医院看你的  绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这东西有些异样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我来教你什么叫「Winter sports」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会点啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开演啊  开演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡扯些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  差不多就到最佳时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在策划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也烧得太久了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的最佳时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等叻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「久等叻」你个头啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂风情的小鬼给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  这可是下雪天才能享受到的热水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上…这开放感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍温了一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太温了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再烧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样泡澡的也只有自家的浴缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话别这么刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一会再出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雪之夜第二幕现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得安心了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下着雪  却窝在被炉里吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  停电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  马上就修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴喊喊就能暖和起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为冷才喊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不会停太长时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那之前还活着的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我有点困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干粮  通信又断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能死在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋千秋…快说啊  那句台词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦  只有一亿元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  那是什么场景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  貌似有这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很冷了你就不能消停一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室  应该还有点余温  去暖一会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑浴也不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变凉了  而且窗户没关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把窗户打开的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是我  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把窗户关上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来  会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把窗户关上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有点恶心能不能别捏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样取暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个取暖方法就够好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了  想吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有倒是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗  我要吃我想吃一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻得硬邦邦可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了那个  都凉到骨子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有热水也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用  因为没煤气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小麦粉  水和鸡蛋搅在一起会有烤薄饼的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做做看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复还真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时不觉得有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没电原来这么不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下这么大的雪居然停电就是松散的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫来想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好教育他一番好让类似的事别发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点子不错  好好地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩晴天娃娃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  偶尔这样过一晚也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  冬木爸爸不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么担心他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定有很多取暖设备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小孩睡得也太早了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对方是小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看上去是那样…春香  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道发生什么怪事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  可能已经睡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为邻居要互相帮助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木遇到什么麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲了很久都没出来  还以为你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开这种不吉利的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正担心冬木你一个人该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家为什么不马上开门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我刚想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这一身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚想换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  把小炉子用的燃气罐借我们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连替换的都有啊  真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了冬木  到我们家玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下小炉子也能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  不用客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秉烛夜谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不知道爸爸什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雪天回到家见我不在  肯定会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很想来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个能干的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一个人应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  突然怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么不想来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样  怕爸爸担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是边说边在想怎么拒绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不老老实实说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样  我并不是很想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这德性我就生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…就别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？想说什么就大声说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏奈姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦  两位准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和他分在一组
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心别人了  赶快还击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样完全不能还击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样组队完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我来扔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责捏雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火就觉得暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感谢文明的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也多亏了冬木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得  就住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缓和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要不是停电也不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这样取暖就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  好像来电了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木在铲雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错  真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这么个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫肉球摸起来真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似根据猫生活的环境  软度也会有所不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猫常常在坚硬的路面上走  肉球也就硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:45.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第7碗  「越嚼越甜哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家猫就软软的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下次试着摸摸肉球吧
